    "title": "Greenery Perception Survey (Quintana et al., 2026)",
    "description": "Based on: Quintana, M., Liu, F., Torkko, J., Gu, Y., Liang, X., Hou, Y., Ito, K., Zhu, Y., Abdelrahman, M., Toivonen, T., Lu, Y., & Biljecki, F. (2026). It is not always greener on the other side: Greenery perception across demographics and personalities in multiple cities. Landscape and Urban Planning, 271, 105618. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.landurbplan.2026.105618. Survey structure follows SPECS (Quintana et al., 2025): demographics, Big Five, and greenery pairwise comparisons (“Which place looks greener?”).",
